<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Dear Investors,<o:p=
></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We are writing to i=
nform you of a recent attempted fraud incident involving one of our investo=
rs. In this case, a third party gained unauthorized access to the investor=
=92s email account and sent a falsified
 version of our capital call notice. The fraudulent notice included <b>alte=
red bank account details</b>, directing funds to an illegitimate account.<o=
:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">PLEASE NOTE THAT=
 THE FUND HAS NOT CHANGED ITS BANK ACCOUNT DETAILS.</span></b><span style=
=3D"font-size:11.0pt"> All legitimate capital call notices from us will ref=
erence the same account information you
 have previously used.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To protect yourself=
 and your organization against similar threats, we ask that you please foll=
ow these precautions:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><b><span style=3D=
"font-size:11.0pt">Always verify any changes in bank account details verbal=
ly with us</span></b><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">, using contact infor=
mation you already have on file =96
<b>do not rely on contact details provided in any email</b> or document, as=
 these may also be fraudulent.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoNormal=
" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Be ale=
rt to any unexpected or unusual emails requesting fund transfers or account=
 changes, especially those marked as urgent.<o:p></o:p></span></li><li clas=
s=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3"><span style=3D"font-size:=
11.0pt">If in doubt,
<b>pause and call us directly</b> to confirm the authenticity of the reques=
t.<o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We take security an=
d investor communication seriously and are implementing additional internal=
 measures to protect against these types of threats. If you have any questi=
ons or concerns, please don=92t hesitate
 to contact us directly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank you<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Eran Raz<o:p></o:p>=
</span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></=
span></p>
